OOC: Thanks for the welcome :), and very nice post.

BIC:

Speedbreaker's face began to show signs of worry, he started to shift 
it around frantically, looking around confused, and worried. "Uhhh, 
stay back," He said in a fearful tone, he had never seen this kind of 
behaviour. He backed up against a wall, and held his gun out.

From around a corner a low below emerged, "Huhhhh, what dis" and 
Beastbox walked around the corner. The small robot looked up, and 
growled, "You right, Decepticons not wimps, let me show you," and he 
leapt up, and towards the captive.
